# Web Components layer

Light DOM only — **never** `attachShadow`.

## Pattern

```ts
// index.ts — CSS side-effect first
import '@rgrmdesign/rgrm-ds-css/button';
export { RGRM_BUTTON_TAG, RgrmButtonElement } from './button-element.js';
```

- Tag: `RGRM_<NAME>_TAG = 'rgrm-<name>'`
- Inner element gets BEM classes via core `classNames()`
- `observedAttributes` for all public HTML attributes
- `customElements.define` in `index.ts`
- Register in `apps/storybook/.storybook/registerElements.ts`

## Package registration

- tsup entry + `package.json` export + barrel
- Add `"./dist/<name>/index.js"` to **`sideEffects`** array

Reference: `packages/elements/src/button/`
